quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,97,"“A fi Allāhu búra, dájúdájú àwa kúkú ti wà nínú ìṣìnà pọ́nńbélé"
  26,98,"nígbà tí a fi yín ṣe akẹgbẹ́ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá."
  26,99,"Kò sí ohun tí ó ṣì wá lọ́nà bí kò ṣe àwọn (èṣù) ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀."
  27,70,"Má ṣe banújẹ́ nítorí wọn. Má sì jẹ́ kí ohun tí wọ́n ń dá ní ète kó ìnira bá ọ."
  27,71,"Wọ́n ń wí pé: “Ìgbà wo ni àdéhùn yìí yóò ṣẹ tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo?”"
  27,72,"Sọ pé: “Ó lè jẹ́ pé apá kan ohun tí ẹ̀ ń wá pẹ̀lú ìkánjú ti súnmọ́ yín tán.”"
  28,43,"Dájúdájú A ti fún (Ànábì) Mūsā ní Tírà lẹ́yìn ìgbà tí A ti pa àwọn ìjọ àkọ́kọ́ rẹ́. (Tírà náà jẹ́) ìmọ̀ àmọ̀dájú àti ẹ̀rí fún àwọn ènìyàn, ìmọ̀nà àti ìkẹ́ nítorí kí wọ́n lè lo ìrántí."
  28,44,"Ìwọ kò sí ní ẹ̀bá ìwọ̀-òòrùn nígbà tí A fi ọ̀rọ̀ náà ránṣẹ́ sí (Ànábì) Mūsā. Àti pé ìwọ kò sí nínú àwọn tó wà níbẹ̀."
  28,45,"Ṣùgbọ́n A ṣẹ̀dá àwọn ìran kan tí ẹ̀mí wọn gùn. O ò kúkú gbé láààrin ará ìlú Mọdyan, tí ò ń ké àwọn āyah Wa fún wọn, ṣùgbọ́n Àwa l’à ń rán àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ níṣẹ́."
  29,10,"Ó ń bẹ nínú àwọn ènìyàn, ẹni tó ń wí pé: “A gba Allāhu gbọ́.” Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sì fi ìnira kàn án nínú ẹ̀sìn Allāhu, ó máa mú ìnira àwọn ènìyàn gẹ́gẹ́ bí ìyà ti Allāhu. (Ó sì máa padà sínú àìgbàgbọ́.) Tí àrànṣe kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ bá sì dé, dájúdájú wọn yóò wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwa wà pẹ̀lú yín.” Ṣé Allāhu kọ́ l’Ó nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ohun tí ń bẹ nínú igbá-àyà gbogbo ẹ̀dá ni?"
  29,11,"Dájúdájú Allāhu máa ṣàfi hàn àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. Ó sì máa ṣàfi hàn àwọn ṣọ̀be-ṣèlu mùsùlùmí."
  29,12,"Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ wí fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo pé: “Ẹ tẹ̀lé ojú ọ̀nà tiwa nítorí kí á lè ru àwọn ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ yín.” Wọn kò sì lè ru kiní kan nínú ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ wọn. Dájúdájú òpùrọ́ mà ni wọ́n."